225F1"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Trailer_End_Card-Recovered.png", "id": "273391962004750", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974788_273391965338083_1886064065722113930_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xMA_C-Jf0PEQ7kNvgE7Yg92&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB8G_dbHRHW8RHhkVOmE-D2vNfCMv7K2T1tYeFVWfZuIA&oe=67221632"}, "display_name": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures", "keywords": ["Cockpit", "Alien", "Green", "Space", "Physics"], "long_description": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures is a VR cockpit game combining ship management with action-arcade combat. You play as a (sometimes effective) bounty hunter with possibly questionable morals, currently in possession of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?\n\n\u2022 Become one with the ship: Immerse yourself in a cockpit packed full from ceiling to floor with distinct physics-based interactions (Though make sure to keep your eye on them all if you want to survive!).\n\n\u2022 Rebel against The Empire: Engage in thrilling dogfights as squads of enemies pursue you to re-capture the small green treasure aboard your ship - shoot bullets, launch bombs, and raise your shields. It's going to get bumpy!\n\n\u2022 Navigate the vacuum of space: Control the ship with a radical and easy-to-use virtual flight stick design, dodge your way through hazardous space environments, and don't forget to do a barrel roll!\n\n\u2022 The little guy: Who could forget your cosmic friend, Ziggy?! This mysterious creature is a perfect fuel source. You can also play with them, use them as a resource, feed them, and most importantly pet them!\n\n\u2022 The Journey: Fight your way through 13 unique levels total. Forge a different path each time by beating challenges and unlocking harder worlds en route.", "short_description": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures is a VR cockpit game combining ship management with action-arcade combat. You play as a (sometimes effective) bounty hunter with possibly questionable morals, currently in possession of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1324311035174797", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_1324311038508130_2610060411856834928_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IF0YPYU0_hYQ7kNvgFHQLlO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDf-gtRwVp_QbCppm_Rc3GARmYkQ-47g3tqpVoy6tzyHA&oe=67220EF8"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Portrait.png", "id": "1021944422558335", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031612_1021944425891668_3460677483354056217_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QQWLjfp2Iz4Q7kNvgFFZNz8&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAz_ctT_6DVyLL-DoaquVD2SvV4htqoasWlxzxrsoFRWQ&oe=67220EFE"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Square.png", "id": "998366967853309", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031369_998366971186642_4701792016341896524_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8SSe19u-hSIQ7kNvgF0ppSG&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBIR9qP8_CkSlvHU7QVKAeZQB-lcr4_u2rdFVlK2Ucg1w&oe=67221C43"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "973425620588096", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610716_973425627254762_5218087471640407679_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SBDPUdU9aUkQ7kNvgHzSRcD&_nc_z